---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About — SearchRank">

<section class="pt-32 pb-20 px-6">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6">About <span class="gradient-text">SearchRank</span></h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="text-lg text-muted mb-8">
        SearchRank was born from a simple observation: traditional SEO agencies are slow, expensive, and opaque.
        Meanwhile, AI can crawl, analyze, and optimize a website faster than any human team — but nobody had
        productized it into a managed service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        Make professional SEO accessible to every business. No retainers, no black-box strategies, no
        meetings about meetings. Just AI-powered optimization that delivers measurable results — weekly.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Why AI-Operated?</h2>
      <p class="text-muted mb-4">
        Traditional agencies charge $2,000–$10,000/month for a team of specialists. That overhead
        pays for salaries, not results. SearchRank uses AI to handle the heavy lifting — crawling,
        content research, drafting, and optimization — at a fraction of the cost.
      </p>
      <p class="text-muted mb-8">
        You still get human oversight, strategic direction, and final approval on everything. The AI
        does the work; you and our team make the calls.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">The Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
        {[
          { label: 'Hosting', value: 'Cloudflare Pages (Global Edge)' },
          { label: 'Crawler', value: 'Custom AI Crawler Engine' },
          { label: 'Content', value: 'LLM-Powered Research & Writing' },
          { label: 'Monitoring', value: 'Prometheus + Grafana' },
          { label: 'Deployment', value: 'GitOps with Argo CD' },
          { label: 'Infrastructure', value: 'Kubernetes (k3s)' },
        ].map((item) => (
          <div class="bg-surface rounded-lg p-4">
            <div class="text-xs text-purple-400 mb-1">{item.label}</div>
            <div class="text-sm">{item.value}</div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4">Based in Florida</h2>
      <p class="text-muted">
        Proudly operating from the Sunshine State. We serve businesses across the US —
        from local shops to national brands.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
